---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for PaperTrends - Learn about the terms and conditions for using our service." canonical="/terms">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-container">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h1 class="heading-primary">
            Terms of Service
          </h1>
          <p class="text-body text-lg">
            Last updated: January 1, 2025
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-container">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert">
          <div class="card-elevated p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12">
            <h2 class="heading-secondary">About This Service</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              PaperTrends is a free, open-source tool that analyzes publicly available academic research data to provide insights into research trends. By using this service, you agree to these simple terms.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">What We Provide</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              We analyze publicly available data from arXiv.org and other academic sources to create visualizations and insights about research trends. Our service is designed to help researchers understand patterns in academic research.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">How You Can Use This Service</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-4">
              You may use PaperTrends for:
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body mb-6">
              <li>Academic research and analysis</li>
              <li>Educational purposes</li>
              <li>Personal learning and exploration</li>
              <li>Non-commercial research activities</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">What You Cannot Do</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-4">
              Please do not:
            </p>
            <ul class="text-body mb-6">
              <li>Use the service for any illegal purposes</li>
              <li>Attempt to damage or interfere with the service</li>
              <li>Use automated tools to overload our servers</li>
              <li>Claim our analysis as your own work without attribution</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">Open Source License</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              PaperTrends is released under the MIT License, which means you are free to use, modify, and distribute the software. The full license is available in our GitHub repository.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">Data Sources and Accuracy</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              Our analysis is based on publicly available data from arXiv.org and other academic sources. While we strive for accuracy, we cannot guarantee that all information is complete or up-to-date. Users should verify important information independently.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">No User Accounts Required</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              PaperTrends does not require user registration or accounts. You can use the service anonymously without providing any personal information.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">Service Availability</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              We strive to keep the service available, but we cannot guarantee 100% uptime. The service may be temporarily unavailable due to maintenance, technical issues, or other factors beyond our control.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              We do not collect personal information from users. Please see our Privacy Policy for details about our minimal data practices.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              PaperTrends is provided "as is" without any warranties. We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of the service. This is a free, open-source tool provided for educational and research purposes.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">Changes to These Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              We may update these terms occasionally. Any changes will be posted on this page. Since this is a simple service, changes will be minimal and primarily technical.
            </p>

            <h2 class="heading-secondary">Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-4">
              If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-body mb-2">
                <strong>Email:</strong> tamara1031.hallloween@gmail.com
              </p>
              <p class="text-body mb-2">
                <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://papertrends.otama-playground.com" class="link-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">papertrends.otama-playground.com</a>
              </p>
              <p class="text-body">
                <strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/tamara1031/papertrends-frontend" class="link-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/tamara1031/papertrends-frontend</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <section class="section-last">
      <div class="section-container text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/" class="btn-primary">
            <i class="fas fa-home mr-2"></i>
            Back to Home
          </a>
          <a href="/privacy" class="btn-outline">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt mr-2"></i>
            Privacy Policy
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
